                <i></i><span>武蔵剣友会について</span>
            </a>
        </section>
        <div class="inter-section">
            <img class="rellax" data-rellax-speed="-1" data-rellax-percentage="0.3" src="./img/稽古風景1.JPG" alt="稽古風景">
        </div>
